                    },
                    "body": "I already added this test internally...\nBut the change is not as \"simple\" as expected.\nI also found an other one, which is related to the same issue in background ( not found until now by users ;-) ).\n\nHave to rework very much to fix this issue.\nI will need several days so dont be angry if this will last a little but ;-)",
