                    "created": "2007-02-15T06:58:21.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-02-15T06:58:21.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/13030",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alexadriaanse",
                        "name": "alexadriaanse",
                        "displayName": "Alex Adriaanse",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Thanks for fixing this.  I can confirm that addYears works fine in ZF 0.8.0.\n\nHowever, addMonths still seems to exhibit the same problem:\n\n{code}\n$date = new Zend_Date('2008-01-01', Zend_Date::ISO_8601);\nprint \"2008-01-01 => $date\\n\";\n$date->addMonth(12);\nprint \"2008-01-01 + 12 months => $date\\n\";\n{code}\n\nReturns:\n{noformat}\n2008-01-01 => Jan 1, 2008 12:00:00 AM\n2008-01-01 + 12 months => Dec 31, 2008 12:00:00 AM\n{noformat}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alexadriaanse",
                        "name": "alexadriaanse",
                        "displayName": "Alex Adriaanse",
